nodes.text: Nathan Karl Kress (born November 18, 1992) is an American actor, director and former professional child model best known for his role as Freddie Benson on the Nickelodeon series iCarly. He provided the voice for Wedge Antilles in LEGO Star Wars: The Force Awakens and the third season and fourth of Star Wars Rebels.
